595
01:11:12.958 --> 01:11:15.542
[CROWD SHOUTING]

596
01:11:27.250 --> 01:11:29.167
[CROWD CHEERS]

597
01:11:40.250 --> 01:11:42.500
[BOTH GRUNTING]

598
01:11:52.292 --> 01:11:54.000
Come on! Come on!

599
01:12:04.167 --> 01:12:05.792
[BOTH GRUNTING]

600
01:12:12.833 --> 01:12:17.083
[FRANK YELLING]

601
01:12:20.500 --> 01:12:21.708
[CROWD CHEERING]

602
01:12:23.250 --> 01:12:26.750
ALL: [CHANTING]
Dux! Dux! Dux!

603
01:12:27.167 --> 01:12:29.333
Well done.

604
01:12:55.125 --> 01:12:59.250
[REFEREE SHOUTING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

605
01:13:00.125 --> 01:13:01.500
[SHOUTS IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

606
01:13:30.417 --> 01:13:32.083
[GROANS]

607
01:13:35.917 --> 01:13:39.500
[CROWD BOOING]

608
01:14:17.250 --> 01:14:21.542
ALL: [CHANTING]
Chong Li! Chong Li! Chong Li!

609
01:15:02.208 --> 01:15:04.083
You are next!

610
01:15:20.208 --> 01:15:23.292
[CROWD CHATTERING]

611
01:15:34.000 --> 01:15:37.542
Prepare the platform
for the final match.

612
01:15:39.083 --> 01:15:42.625
This is it, Frank.
You can make history here today.

613
01:15:50.250 --> 01:15:54.417
[ALL CHATTERING]

614
01:15:56.667 --> 01:16:00.417
Frank, you OK?

615
01:16:00.583 --> 01:16:03.250
- Frank?
- Yeah.

616
01:17:08.167 --> 01:17:10.042
[SHOUTS IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

617
01:17:15.000 --> 01:17:17.208
[SHOUTS IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

618
01:17:29.667 --> 01:17:31.542
[REFEREE SHOUTS
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

619
01:17:32.667 --> 01:17:34.875
[REFEREE SHOUTS
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

620
01:17:35.167 --> 01:17:39.083
You break my record, now I break you

621
01:17:39.250 --> 01:17:41.125
like I break your friend.

622
01:17:46.833 --> 01:17:48.250
[SNIFFS]

623
01:17:54.167 --> 01:17:55.042
[SHOUTS IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

624
01:17:56.917 --> 01:18:00.000
[CROWD SHOUTING]

625
01:18:19.833 --> 01:18:24.292
[BOTH GRUNTING]

626
01:18:26.417 --> 01:18:28.208
Get him, Dux.
Come on.

627
01:18:33.250 --> 01:18:36.500
[BOTH GRUNTING]

628
01:18:40.333 --> 01:18:41.875
Come on!
Get up, Frank!

629
01:18:49.750 --> 01:18:54.542
[BOTH GRUNTING]

630
01:19:00.458 --> 01:19:04.667
CROWD: [CHANTING]
Chong Li! Chong Li! Chong Li!

631
01:19:07.583 --> 01:19:12.250
CROWD: [CHANTING]
Dux! Dux! Dux!

632
01:19:14.875 --> 01:19:16.125
[GRUNTS]

633
01:19:16.292 --> 01:19:18.125
[YELLING]

634
01:19:18.292 --> 01:19:20.708
- Right on.
- Come on now, Dux. Come on.

635
01:19:40.792 --> 01:19:43.625
[BOTH GRUNTING]

636
01:19:53.958 --> 01:19:57.250
[CROWD CHEERING]

637
01:19:58.208 --> 01:19:59.542
More! More!

638
01:20:12.208 --> 01:20:15.375
[GRUNTS]

639
01:20:20.417 --> 01:20:23.500
[BOTH GRUNTING]

640
01:20:39.167 --> 01:20:41.542
[YELLS]

641
01:20:42.500 --> 01:20:44.292
[CROWD GASPS]

642
01:20:44.917 --> 01:20:46.958
[FRANK GROANS]

643
01:20:49.958 --> 01:20:53.167
[FRANK GROANING]

644
01:20:54.417 --> 01:20:56.083
Up! Up!

645
01:21:06.042 --> 01:21:12.000
CROWD: [CHANTING]
Chong Li! Chong Li! Chong Li!

646
01:21:17.375 --> 01:21:19.250
[FRANK GROANING]

647
01:21:25.542 --> 01:21:27.500
[CHONG LI YELLS]

648
01:21:41.500 --> 01:21:44.625
[YELLING]

649
01:21:50.125 --> 01:21:51.500
Get up, Frankie!

650
01:22:03.500 --> 01:22:07.458
[SCREAMING]

651
01:22:52.833 --> 01:22:54.083
[GRUNTS]

652
01:22:54.250 --> 01:22:56.292
[BOTH GRUNTING]

653
01:22:59.250 --> 01:23:01.875
[CROWD SHOUTING]

654
01:23:17.458 --> 01:23:18.917
[GRUNTS]

655
01:23:39.125 --> 01:23:40.500
All right.

656
01:23:41.792 --> 01:23:43.083
[ALL SHOUTING]

657
01:24:10.500 --> 01:24:13.125
[BOTH GRUNTING]

658
01:24:33.750 --> 01:24:38.500
[GROANING]

659
01:24:41.917 --> 01:24:43.208
[YELLING]

660
01:24:43.375 --> 01:24:44.458
[ALL CHEERING AND SHOUTING]

661
01:24:47.167 --> 01:24:48.792
Say it!

662
01:24:50.708 --> 01:24:52.417
Say it!

663
01:24:53.875 --> 01:24:55.375
Say it!

664
01:24:55.542 --> 01:24:58.083
<i>Mate.</i>

665
01:24:58.458 --> 01:24:59.500
[CROWD CHEERING]

666
01:24:59.667 --> 01:25:01.250
All right!

667
01:25:02.000 --> 01:25:03.250
[ALL CHEERING]

668
01:25:05.000 --> 01:25:09.833
CROWD: [CHANTING]
Dux! Dux! Dux!

669
01:25:12.542 --> 01:25:14.250
[MOUTHING]
Yeah, Frankie.

670
01:25:24.083 --> 01:25:27.833
MAN: Mr. Dux, you fought
with inspiration.

671
01:25:28.000 --> 01:25:31.333
We of the <i>Kokoruki</i> salute you.

672
01:25:50.750 --> 01:25:52.958
This is for you, <i>shidoshi.</i>

673
01:25:55.583 --> 01:25:57.958
So you stomped him real good, Frankie?

674
01:25:58.125 --> 01:26:01.708
- JANICE: Worse.
- What do you mean?

675
01:26:03.042 --> 01:26:04.708
He made him say <i>mate.</i>

676
01:26:06.667 --> 01:26:08.917
All right, Frankie!

677
01:26:09.083 --> 01:26:11.792
But don't you get too cocky

678
01:26:11.958 --> 01:26:14.500
'cause you might have
to go up against me next time.

679
01:26:14.667 --> 01:26:16.125
- FRANK: I promise.
- Mm-hm.

680
01:26:16.292 --> 01:26:19.333
You guys are out of your minds.

681
01:26:19.500 --> 01:26:22.375
- I'll drink to that!
- JANICE: Ha, ha!

682
01:26:22.542 --> 01:26:24.833
By the way, next time you fight,

683
01:26:25.000 --> 01:26:27.875
try to keep your clothes on.

684
01:26:32.583 --> 01:26:36.792
Anytime, anyplace, anywhere.

685
01:26:36.958 --> 01:26:40.333
If you ever need me,
I'll be there.

686
01:26:43.542 --> 01:26:45.667
I love you, my friend.

687
01:26:50.292 --> 01:26:51.792
Me, too.

688
01:26:56.583 --> 01:26:58.083
Take care.

689
01:26:58.458 --> 01:27:00.667
[SIGHS]

690
01:27:09.583 --> 01:27:11.042
[HELMER SCOFFS]

691
01:27:11.208 --> 01:27:13.500
He's not going to show.

692
01:27:13.667 --> 01:27:15.667
Looks like he did it to us again, huh?

693
01:27:17.708 --> 01:27:18.542
[FRANK WHISTLES]

694
01:27:18.708 --> 01:27:19.667
FRANK: Hey, guys!

695
01:27:19.833 --> 01:27:21.708
You coming or what?

696
01:27:21.875 --> 01:27:23.375
[HELMER CHUCKLES]

697
01:27:23.542 --> 01:27:25.667
You son of a bitch.

698
01:27:25.833 --> 01:27:28.250
You're always late!

699
01:27:32.708 --> 01:27:36.083
You know, you're really
a pain in the ass, you know that?

700
01:27:38.833 --> 01:27:41.167
I'm just glad you're on our side, kid.

